                <h1 className="text-6xl sm:text-7xl font-black mb-6 leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter">Pure focus, <br/><span className="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-500">zero noise.</span></h1>
